<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/zookeys.1183.113075.figure2>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Copulatory organs of Grandilithus chongzuo sp. nov. A male left palp, prolateral view B same, retrolateral view C same, ventral view D same, dorsal view E epigyne, ventral view F same, dorsal view. Abbreviations: B-bursa; CD-copulatory duct; CO-copulatory opening; CT-connecting tube; E-embolus; FA-femoral apophysis; FD-fertilization duct; GA-glandular appendage; MS-median septum; RTA-retrolateral tibial apophysis; S-spermatheca; SD-sperm duct; TA-tegular apophysis; Tu-tubercle." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/932447" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

